Question: The left and right image contains the same number of antelope facing opposite directions.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/originals/9c/f3/cb/9cf3cb534a31780628ca5d3bb50ce6b7.jpg

Right image URL: http://www.ultimateungulate.com/Images/Alcelaphus_buselaphus/A_buselaphus3.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many antelope are facing left?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many antelope are facing left?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many antelope are facing right?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many antelope are facing right?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER1} == {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
